However, the item wipe slowed us down nicely in the conquest of the uber monsters, and it will take us couple months to be able to really hunt in ToV, kill Dain, Velketor, and the really big guns in Kael. Once we have the items from those, we will be able to to hunt in sleeper and all.<br>
As a side note, we are NOT aware of 80% of the changes Verant makes, so we can't really test them directly.<br>
To conclude, please do not consider Test players as wussy players that can't test anything. Lots of us are good players, we just have less players, less items, no platinum economy at ALL, barely any trade economy since the loot goes to those who needs it usually.<br>
