Of course, VI's refusal to test a number of things to preserve the mystery doesn't help. (Loot tables, Sleeper's, Siren's, PoM, PoG et cetera.) The only mystery is why people don't complain more.</td></tr></table><br><p>[ No Comments Allowed for Anonymous, please <a href="user.php">register</a>  ]</font><p></ul></p><a name="994"></a><table width=99% border=0><tr bgcolor="#efefef"><td width=500><p><b>Re: Put a uber guild on test server?</b> <font size=2>(Score: 1)<br>by Kreugen on Thursday, March 08 @ 17:14:22 EST<br>(<a href="user.php?op=userinfo&uname=Kreugen">User Info</a>) </font></td></tr><tr><td>Yeah we don't take enough shit for nonexistant favoritism as it is.<br>
